309
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:51,520
I don't need a reward.

310
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,880
I only wish to take on a disciple.

311
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:56,840
Once she wakes up,

312
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:58,480
