320
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,560
I told you,

321
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:17,120
I'm not your master.

322
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,360
Yes, sir.

323
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:19,840
